  "Sanctions" : "REQUIRED TO REQUALIFY AS A GENERAL SECURITIES PRINCIPAL BY TAKING AN PASSING THE SERIES 24 EXAMINATION NO LATER THAN 60 DAYS FOLLOWING THE DATE OF THIS DECISION; AND, RESPONDENT GALLAGHER IS ASSESSED DBCC PROCEEDING COSTS OF $1,356.70, JOINTLY AND SEVERALLY.  ADDITION, WITHIN 60 DAYS OF THE DATE OF THIS DECISION, RESPONDENT GALLAGHER MUST DEMONSTRATE TO THE STAFF OF THE DISTRICT 2 OFFICE OF NASD REGULATION, INC. THAT HE HAS PUT INTO PLACE A SYSTEM TO SUPERVISE THE ACTIVITIES OF THE FIRM'S OFFICE OF SUPERVISORY JURISDICTION. ** ",
